microbrain — names-ladder.log: the full ladder (train0-train5) re-run on Karpathy's names corpus
provenance: fresh clone of this repo; python data/make_dataset.py --names (32,033 names -> 29,494 unique docs, vocab 27); then python trainN.py for n=0..5, full budgets, same seeds
purpose: measure which parts of the course's story are corpus-independent — see the README's corpus paragraph

